videos.headline: No. 7 UT holds off No. 13 Maryland's second-half surge
videos.description: Led by Zakai Zeigler and Tyreke Key, Tennessee holds off the Terrapins' strong second half to finish with a 56-53 win in the Top-10 matchup.
